title: Pull request merge from jgors/nilearn:master to nilearn/nilearn:master

text:
> thought that was already done from looking at AlexandreAbraham comment.

No, Alex just did a review and said that it looked fine to him. We tend
to ask for two independent reviews before a merge. At least if we do
things by the book, where the book is the scikit-learn development
guidelines.
oh, oops...thought that was already done from looking at AlexandreAbraham comment.  anyways, thanks and looking forward to hacking along with nilearn!
Plus, I am not the one with the best english level.
